title: Good late game duelists season 6
body: Besides jax and nasus and only melee champions.

replies.body: Tryndamere, Warwick, Yi, Trundle, Udyr, Xin Zhao.
You can probably add Fiora and Yasuo onto that list as well, though the latter will usually lose a straight punch-up with Tryn and Yi.
Yeah...there are more than the ones I mentioned...just just immediately came in my mind. The top 5 are probably Nasus, Jax, Yi, Tryndamere and Warwick though.
